# Auth Navigation Ownership

- Route protection belongs in route middleware.
- Post-login redirect behavior belongs in the login page or auth-specific utilities.
- Do **not** add app-wide auth watchers in `app.vue` that push users between routes.
- Keep login redirect helpers pure and testable.
